p1146
aVLike you can have a service listening for trade notifications and persist just the ones it's interested in (aggregating in memory if required)
p1147
aVYou can do open/high/low/close prices this way
p1148
aVFor high volume data you don't really want to write it all to the database
p1149
aVNot synchronously anyway
p1150
aVA persistent store plus a data warehouse is probably more the route you 
