aVcircumstances, doubling the number of
p3639
aValgorithms looking for hidden data can
p3640
aVincrease the capacity of the
p3641
aVsteganographic channel
p3642
aVIn other words, the more algorithms you use to identify messages the less effective it becomes, which goes against the normal criticism of security through obscurity
