VThe way to handle this kind of situation is to not to cache writes from multiple places or to control access in some other way
p17742
aVA simple solution to this is to not do any writes to the cache from your clients
p17743
aVInstead if you want to update the value you fire off a request to have the value updated
p17744
aVIf that value is retrieved from somewhere else then this can work well
p17745
