aVA racing game might go into more detail about the wheels, such as how hot they are, how worn, the width and tread type and so on
p23943
aVIn such a case, a Wheel object could be said to be a collection of all that state (but little behaviour) because a Car has a number of Wheels and the Wheels are interchangeable
p23944
aVSo that brings up the second point about objects: an object can exist because of a relationship such that the object represents a complete set of data
p23945
aVSo a Wheel could have tread, width, temperature and so on
