aVVariable Base Encoding
p24798
aVIn legal boards certain pieces can\u2019t appear in certain squares
p24799
aVFor example, pawns cannot occur at in the first or eighth ranks, reducing the possibilities for those squares to 11
p24800
aVThat reduces the possible boards to 1116 x 1348 = 1
